    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tropical forests characterized by dense canopies of broad-leaved trees and other vegetation that form three different layers; located in areas having no dry season; an example is the Amazon rainforest in Brazil.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
